<section class="sd-section"><h2>Authorized dealer and UPP/MAP policy</h2><p>Sinister Mfg. Company, Inc. (Sinister Diesel&reg;) is committed to protecting the integrity, performance and reputation of its brand. The signature blue finish, distinctive logo and product line represent quality, innovation and diesel performance.</p><p>To preserve that value and provide a consistent customer experience, Sinister Diesel maintains a Unilateral Pricing Policy (UPP) and Minimum Advertised Price (MAP) Policy. These policies support customers, authorized resellers and the long-term equity of the brand.</p></section>
<section class="sd-section"><h2>Why buy from an authorized dealer?</h2><p>Products purchased directly from Sinister Diesel or an authorized dealer provide a verified ownership path:</p><div class="sd2-policy__benefits"><article><span>01</span><strong>Genuine products</strong><p>Authentic Sinister Diesel products that meet current quality standards.</p></article><article><span>02</span><strong>Warranty coverage</strong><p>Coverage subject to the current warranty policy and eligibility requirements.</p></article><article><span>03</span><strong>Product support</strong><p>Access to customer service, technical support and current product resources.</p></article><article><span>04</span><strong>Complete documentation</strong><p>Installation information, product updates and troubleshooting resources when available.</p></article></div></section>
<section class="sd-section"><h2>Risks of unauthorized sellers</h2><p>Products offered through unauthorized sellers may be used, counterfeit, altered, incomplete, outside warranty coverage or ineligible for Sinister Diesel technical support and returns.</p><div class="sd2-policy__notice"><strong>Verify before purchasing</strong><p>To the extent permitted by law, Sinister Diesel may deny technical support, warranty coverage or customer service for products purchased through unauthorized channels. Support inquiries may be referred to the original seller.</p></div></section>
<section class="sd-section"><h2>Policy enforcement and dealer responsibility</h2><p>Direct or indirect sale of Sinister Diesel products to unauthorized resellers may violate the UPP/MAP Policy and can result in suspension or termination of dealer privileges.</p><p>Sinister Diesel monitors online and offline sales channels to support compliance and preserve brand integrity. We appreciate the continued partnership of authorized dealers.</p></section>
